race.comment: GRAY ELLIOT (6) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.5 lengths from the winner Smooth Ranger in third(26.05) at this track. One of the contenders. SAINT TAY (1) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (22.60) at this track. Can measure up this time. MAXIMUM REED (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 2.75 lengths (22.83) at this track. Worth following up. JAZZY HOPE (7) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.
